{"parentUuid":"54fd2d7d-7f4f-4c73-8796-8fae99a6b0c2","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"4309ba94-9fe4-48ca-8d5f-17e8661d71b6","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QVTJ5WDYchVWcj3DRbv1U7","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# 孤儿页\n2\t\n3\t完全没有被其他 wiki 页 / raw / chats 引用的 wiki 页。常见原因:新建后忘记补链;真的没人需要(候选废弃)。\n4\t\n5\t相关:[[tombstone-candidates]]、[[single-source]]\n6\t\n7\t```dataview\n8\tTABLE WITHOUT ID file.link as \"页面\", type, created, length(file.outlinks) as \"Outbound\"\n9\tFROM \"wiki\" AND !\"wiki/dataviews\"\n10\tWHERE length(file.inlinks) = 0\n11\t  AND file.name != \"index\" AND file.name != \"log\"\n12\tSORT type ASC, file.name ASC\n13\t```\n14\t"}]},"uuid":"b617b28d-360d-4938-9418-2a1490ec4346","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:42:24.128Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"wiki/dataviews/orphans.md","content":"# 孤儿页\n\n完全没有被其他 wiki 页 / raw / chats 引用的 wiki 页。常见原因:新建后忘记补链;真的没人需要(候选废弃)。\n\n相关:[[tombstone-candidates]]、[[single-source]]\n\n```dataview\nTABLE WITHOUT ID file.link as \"页面\", type, created, length(file.outlinks) as \"Outbound\"\nFROM \"wiki\" AND !\"wiki/dataviews\"\nWHERE length(file.inlinks) = 0\n  AND file.name != \"index\" AND file.name != \"log\"\nSORT type ASC, file.name ASC\n```\n","numLines":14,"startLine":1,"totalLines":14}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"54fd2d7d-7f4f-4c73-8796-8fae99a6b0c2","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-ts","cwd":"/Users/wille/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/Docs/Obsidian/digital playground/digital playground","sessionId":"d87ee1eb-d45b-41bd-aecd-3c1ae0cf0a9d","version":"2.1.132","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
