{"parentUuid":"59c2bfc0-754c-45cc-9100-d87ad0811d06","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"4309ba94-9fe4-48ca-8d5f-17e8661d71b6","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018tDU2s63bALVj3xyHBN4xK","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# 热度排行\n2\t\n3\t被引用最多的 wiki 页(top 15)。活跃概念信号。\n4\t\n5\t更强的活跃信号见 [[raw-backlinks]](只看 raw/chats 反向引用,过滤 wiki 内部互链)。\n6\t\n7\t```dataview\n8\tTABLE WITHOUT ID file.link as \"页面\", type, length(file.inlinks) as \"Inbound\"\n9\tFROM \"wiki\" AND !\"wiki/dataviews\"\n10\tWHERE length(file.inlinks) > 0\n11\t  AND file.name != \"index\" AND file.name != \"log\"\n12\tSORT length(file.inlinks) DESC\n13\tLIMIT 15\n14\t```\n15\t"}]},"uuid":"4830395d-6fb1-4fdf-852b-7a6f3dcc21fa","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:42:24.827Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"wiki/dataviews/most-cited.md","content":"# 热度排行\n\n被引用最多的 wiki 页(top 15)。活跃概念信号。\n\n更强的活跃信号见 [[raw-backlinks]](只看 raw/chats 反向引用,过滤 wiki 内部互链)。\n\n```dataview\nTABLE WITHOUT ID file.link as \"页面\", type, length(file.inlinks) as \"Inbound\"\nFROM \"wiki\" AND !\"wiki/dataviews\"\nWHERE length(file.inlinks) > 0\n  AND file.name != \"index\" AND file.name != \"log\"\nSORT length(file.inlinks) DESC\nLIMIT 15\n```\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":15}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"59c2bfc0-754c-45cc-9100-d87ad0811d06","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-ts","cwd":"/Users/wille/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/Docs/Obsidian/digital playground/digital playground","sessionId":"d87ee1eb-d45b-41bd-aecd-3c1ae0cf0a9d","version":"2.1.132","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"4830395d-6fb1-4fdf-852b-7a6f3dcc21fa","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01MnDPaJzxpRVzM42Yy9pemY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 测试结论\n\n**两个问题都已验证,答案都是负面的:**\n\n### 1. 只能读到查询代码,读不到渲染结果\n\n我用 Read 工具读取了 `wiki/dataviews/` 下的三个文件(`orphans.md`、`type-distribution.md`、`most-cited.md`),返回的内容**只有原始的 markdown + DQL 查询代码块**(```` ```dataview ... ``` ````),**没有任何渲染后的表格数据**。\n\n原因:Dataview 是 Obsidian 插件的运行时渲染,结果只存在于 Obsidian 应用内存中,从不写回 `.md` 文件。Read 工具读的是磁盘上的原文,看到的永远是查询代码本身。\n\n### 2. \"实时 vs 缓存\"这个问题不适用\n\n既然根本读不到渲染结果,也就谈不上\"实时 vs 之前渲染过的结果\"——每次 Read 拿到的都是同一份静态的查询源代码。即使你在 Obsidian 里刚刚打开过这些视图、看到了最新结果,LLM 这边也完全看不到。\n\n### 影响 — `CLAUDE.md` 的 Lint workflow 需要修正\n\n`CLAUDE.md` 的 [Lint](#lint) 章节写着:\n\n> **1. 先扫一遍 `wiki/dataviews/` 下相关的 view 页**——机械检查已经被 Dataview 覆盖,**直接读结果**,不要手工 grep 重复\n\n这一行**实际上做不到**。LLM 读 view 文件只能拿到 DQL 源码,拿不到结果。可选的修复方向:\n\n1. **手动转译 DQL 为 LLM 可执行的等价操作**(Glob/Grep/Read frontmatter 自己算孤儿、单源等)——本质上又回到了\"手工 grep\",违背了 view 的初衷。\n2. **让用户把 view 结果导出**(例如复制粘贴渲染后的表格到 view 文件下方的\"## 最近一次快照\"区块,或用 Dataview 的 `dataviewjs` + 文件 API 写回磁盘——但这会污染 markdown 清洁度)。\n3. **接受现状**:Dataview view 是给人看的,Lint 时由用户先在 Obsidian 里打开 view、把结果贴给 LLM,LLM 再做 step 2 的语义判断。\n\n要不要现在就更新 `CLAUDE.md` 的 Lint 章节,把这个限制写进去(以及选定一种 workflow)?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":992,"cache_read_input_tokens":28851,"output_tokens":880,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":992,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":880,"cache_read_input_tokens":28851,"cache_creation_input_tokens":992,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":992},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cb5dnsM728GAodXZcTVCh","type":"