{"parentUuid":"cc724479-d1ff-4579-82a8-27bcd100809b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01GPFTAqucnQvSwGj7J2e5vr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":913,"cache_read_input_tokens":29843,"output_tokens":2939,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":913,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":2939,"cache_read_input_tokens":29843,"cache_creation_input_tokens":913,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":913},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cb5frzMsoGq4roPo7ZNLo","type":"assistant","uuid":"6449d75c-830f-4eb2-9ca6-df30bd91a548","timestamp":"2026-05-16T05:09:54.708Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-ts","cwd":"/Users/wille/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/Docs/Obsidian/digital playground/digital playground","sessionId":"d87ee1eb-d45b-41bd-aecd-3c1ae0cf0a9d","version":"2.1.132","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"6449d75c-830f-4eb2-9ca6-df30bd91a548","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01GPFTAqucnQvSwGj7J2e5vr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 让 Agent 拿到实时 Dataview 结果的几种办法\n\n按\"实用度 × 落地成本\"排序:\n\n---\n\n## 方案 A: 用 Python 脚本重新实现这 10 个查询(推荐)\n\n**核心思路**:这些 view 都很简单——读 frontmatter、扫 wikilinks、按 type/created/inlinks 聚合。完全可以用一个 ~150 行的 Python 脚本复刻,LLM 直接 `Bash` 调用。\n\n```bash\npython wiki/dataviews/_run.py orphans      # 输出与 Dataview 表格等价的 JSON/markdown\npython wiki/dataviews/_run.py most-cited\npython wiki/dataviews/_run.py --all        # Lint 时一把梭\n```\n\n**优点**\n- 完全在 LLM 控制内,不依赖 Obsidian 是否打开。\n- 结果\"实时\"——每次调用都重新扫盘。\n- 可以加 LLM 友好的输出格式(JSON / markdown table)。\n- Lint workflow 真正自动化:`Bash` 跑脚本 → 拿到结构化结果 → 做语义判断。\n\n**缺点**\n- DQL 和 Python 两套实现,要保持一致(但这 10 个 view 都很稳定,迁移完基本不动)。\n- `file.inlinks` 要自己实现(走一遍 vault 把 `[[...]]` 解析出来建反向索引;不难)。\n\n**适合**:Lint 自动化。这是唯一一个能让 `CLAUDE.md` 的 Lint step 1 真正落地的方案。\n\n---\n\n## 方案 B: Obsidian Local REST API plugin + Dataview API\n\n装两个插件:\n- **Local REST API**(`coddingtonbear/obsidian-local-rest-api`)——把 Obsidian 内部暴露成 HTTPS。\n- 配 **Dataview Serializer** 或自己写一段 `dataviewjs` 桥接。\n\nLLM `Bash curl` 一下就能拿 JSON。\n\n**优点**\n- 查询继续用 DQL 写在 view 文件里,Obsidian 侧看效果不变。\n- 真正\"实时\"。\n\n**缺点**\n- **要求 Obsidian 进程在跑**(macOS 后台开着即可)。\n- 需要管理 API token、自签证书。\n- 多一层活动部件——Obsidian 没开就全挂。\n\n**适合**:用户长时间开着 Obsidian + 想保留 DQL 单一源。\n\n---\n\n## 方案 C: Snapshot 模式(快照写回磁盘)\n\n在每个 view 文件里加一个 `dataviewjs` 块,把结果**渲染成 markdown 表格写到磁盘**(同一文件下方的 `## 最近快照` 区块)。\n\n```js\n// dataviewjs\nconst result = await dv.query(`TABLE ... FROM \"wiki\" ...`);\n// 把 result 序列化成 markdown,写回 app.vault.modify(...)\n```\n\n或者用 **Templater** + 一个 hotkey,触发\"刷新全部 view 快照\"。\n\n**优点**\n- LLM 用普通 Read 就能读到结果。\n- 不需要外部进程。\n\n**缺点**\n- \"实时\"打折——只有用户主动触发刷新才会更新。\n- view 文件被自动写入,违反 markdown 清洁度原则。\n- 给 git diff 添噪。\n\n**适合**:折中方案,可以容忍\"半实时\"。\n\n---\n\n## 方案 D: MCP 服务器(`mcp-obsidian` 系列)\n\n社区已有几个 MCP server 把 Obsidian 暴露给 LLM,部分支持 Dataview 查询(例如 `MarkusPfundstein/mcp-obsidian`)。配上后,Claude 这边多一个 `mcp__obsidian__dataview_query` 工具。\n\n**优点**:协议层的解决方案,比 Local REST API 更\"原生\"。\n**缺点**:需要 Obsidian 开着;当前 MCP server 的 Dataview 支持成熟度参差(有的只支持简单 query)。\n\n---\n\n## 我的建议\n\n**走方案 A**。理由:\n1. Lint 是这事的核心场景,要求**无人值守、可重跑、可 grep**——只有脚本满足。\n2. 这 10 个查询都很机械,Python 实现一次就稳定。\n3. 不引入\"Obsidian 必须开着\"这种隐性依赖。\n4. 输出格式可以为 LLM 优化(直接给 markdown 表 + 元信息,LLM 做 step 2 语义判断时更省 token)。\n\n如果你 OK,我可以现在就:\n- 写 `wiki/dataviews/_run.py`(把现有 10 个 DQL 翻成 Python),\n- 在 `CLAUDE.md` Lint 章节把 step 1 改成\"`Bash` 跑 `_run.py --all` 拿到结构化结果\",\n- 顺便在每个 view 文件顶部加一行 `Run: \\`python wiki/dataviews/_run.py <slug>\\`` 当文档。\n\n要继续吗?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":913,"cache_read_input_tokens":29843,"output_tokens":2939,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":913,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":2939,"cache_read_input_tokens":29843,"cache_creation_input_tokens":913,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":913},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cb5frzMsoGq4roPo7ZNLo","type":"assistant","uuid":"831b44cb-2cb0-44bb-aedb-dc72b6e9fa84","timestamp":"2026-05-16T05:10:25.313Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-ts","cwd":"/Users/wille/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/Docs/Obsidian/digital playground/digital playground","sessionId":"d87ee1eb-d45b-41bd-aecd-3c1ae0cf0a9d","version":"2.1.132","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
